title: Marvel Must Haves: Nyx 1-3 (2005) #23
description:
Reprinting the sold-out NYX #4-5, in time for next month’s NYX #6 – plus all-new, never-before-seen extras! With a penchant for attracting strays, newcomer Tatiana picks up more than she bargained for when she manifests a striking mutant ability and catches the attention of Kiden's wayward gang. Plus: What if you could become anyone in the world for a day? What would you do? Who would you be? Captain America fighting alongside the Avengers? Bono during a concert in Wembley Stadium? Meet a young mutant who doesn’t have to wonder. His powers let him be anyone he wants, and he isn’t shy about using them!
80 PGS./ Parental Advisory …$3.99
